{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji26","name":"毛泽东全集第26卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/maoquanji26.pdf"],"article":{"title":"复华东军区电","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"复华东军区电"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1949年2月27日）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们对重庆号的处置是适当的。只要有可能就要争取邓兆祥、陆荣一在政治上站在我们方面，以利争取国民党海军全部归顺过来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东关于国民党海军重庆号巡洋舰起义问题为中共中央军委起草的复华东军区电的主要内容。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[2]邓兆祥、陆荣一，当时分别任重庆号巡洋舰正、副舰长，2月25日"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":2,"day":27}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":166,"page_end":166},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}